Complete the following steps to log in to the Apps Manager:

1. Browse to `apps.YOUR-SYSTEM-DOMAIN`.
In Pivotal Ops Manager, refer to **Pivotal Elastic Runtime > Settings > Domains** to locate your system domain.

1. Log in to the Apps Manager using the UAA Administrator User
credentials.
In Pivotal Ops Manager, refer to **Pivotal Elastic Runtime > Credentials** for
these credentials.